snippet: South African emergency workers rescued eight miners trapped in Harmony Gold’s Doornkop mine but a search went on for nine others still unaccounted for more than a day later.
abstract: South African emergency workers rescue eight miners trapped by fire and rock fall in Harmony Gold’s Doornkop mine but search continues for nine others.
lead_paragraph: South African emergency workers rescued eight miners trapped in Harmony Gold’s Doornkop mine but a search went on for nine others still unaccounted for more than a day later.
